644
00:29:51,420 --> 00:29:52,820
with chicks and ducklings.

645
00:29:53,020 --> 00:29:53,580
And...

646
00:29:53,860 --> 00:29:54,700
They were

647
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:55,980
a family.

648
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:59,300
